name: Pure heart #5
description: Heart, however, did not know at all what he was going to do or who he should talk to. After a while, he got bored and started talking to himself. He began to complain of loneliness and that he wished to have many friends again. When Moon saw he is ready to change she began to shine and clear the darkness of his heart.Now it was a little Fiery fish again. And he can come out of his cave...
